Returns 0 on null input or allocation failure.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "schema_definitions_get_or_create" takes node as Integer returns Integer:
    If node is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    Let defs be proc memory_get_int64 from Memory with node, 40
    If defs is not equal to 0:
        Return defs
    End If
