@Performance_Hints
Time: O(|name|).
@End Performance_Hints

@Security_Scope
Returns 0 on null inputs.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "schema_add_definition" takes node as Integer, name as Integer, schema as Integer returns Integer:
    If name is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    If schema is equal to 0:
        Return 0
    End If
    Let defs be proc schema_definitions_get_or_create with node
    If defs is equal to 0:
